  title="Evil Is Not Banal. It's Chosen."
  description="For decades, psychology offered a comforting story: ordinary people do terrible things because situations overwhelm them. Modern reanalysis of Milgram and the debunking of the Stanford Prison Experiment reveal that the story was wrong — and that the truth is harder to live with."
